      <bioghist id="aspace_3dbc480119a2edd1a3ba50887efac91d">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Charles Wayne Chase was born in Cleveland, Ohio on November 16, 1901.  Mr. Chase majored in administrative engineering at the Sheffield Scientific School at Yale University, graduating in 1923.  While at Yale, Chase was involved with the wrestling and rowing teams, belonged to Berzelius, the Colony, and the Torch Honor Society.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_53ba483d99f70dcbb0da0d3c844bdf48">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of scrapbooks, photographs, newspaper clippings and ephemera of Charles Wayne Chase primarily documenting the Yale Crew Team, rowing and regattas.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
